[0.10] 2021-09-06
 - Update mailing list links to new Google Groups.
 - Convert README from ISO-8859-1 to UTF-8.
 - Switch manpage section from deprecated 1x to 1.
 - Fix multiscreen support.
 - Increase buffer size for string to avoid compiler warning.
 - Use correct type for dotclock from XF86VidModeModeInfo.
 - Check return values from XF86VidMode* for submenus.
 - Display error message if XF86VidModeGetModeLine fails

[0.9] 2017-08-27
 - Now maintained by the Window Maker Team.
 - Rename configure.in -> configure.ac.
 - Remove obselete AC_C_CONST macro.
 - Use pkg-config to find libraries.
 - Use automake.
 - Use wmgeneral from libdockapp.
 - Port to GTK+3.
 - Update GPL2 text.
 - Remove trailing whitespace.
 - Update documentation.

(The original author did not keep a changelog for previous versions.)
